<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>173</hymn_number>
<title>tiān kāi le tiān kāi le 迦南173</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 tiān kāi le tiān kāi le shèng líng xiàng gē zi jiàng xià
 gāo mǒ zhe nǐ yě gèng xīn zhe wǒ shēng mìng de huó shuǐ rú jiāng hé
 tiān shàng de bái gē zhēn lǐ de líng yuàn nǐ yǒng jū zài wǒ men xīn zhōng
 shí cháng wò zhù wǒ men de shǒu dài wǒ men jìn rù yǒng héng
 wǒ men de líng zhēn kě mù rú lù xiàn mù xī shuǐ
 zhǔ de líng zài gāo mǒ wǒ men de xīn yǐ sū xǐng</lyrics>
</song>